"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-athletics-2024-0529-1452036-the-silver-secret-treacys-olympic-marathon-medal\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Have you heard the one about the Irishman who won an Olympic silver medal in his first ever marathon?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 22}, {\"ngram\": \"the Irishman\", \"from\": 29, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic silver medal\", \"from\": 50, \"to\": 73}]}, {\"sentence\": \"40 years ago this August, John Treacy did just that, stunning the athletics world at the Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Treacy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletics world\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"the Los Angeles Games\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Waterford man was best known as a cross-country, 5,000 and 10,000-metre runner, and had put in 20k of hard running to finish ninth in the latter event six days previously.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\", \"score\": 0.9539459571200327, \"rank\": 0.0477191424052153, \"text\": \"Waterford\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cross\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"5,000 and 10,000-metre runner\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"20k\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter event\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Entering an event the 27-year-old had never competed in, it might have seemed like an afterthought or insurance policy.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"an afterthought or insurance policy\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, secretly, it was the target all along.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having moved back to his college town of Providence, Rhode Island the previous autumn in a bid to reignite his running career, Treacy resumed training with his former college coach Bob Amato's group and was introduced to Argentinian cardiologist and marathon runner Dr Dario Herrera.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"score\": 0.9999768590168074, \"rank\": 2.266567194867934e-05, \"text\": \"Providence\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"score\": 0.9999542871281314, \"rank\": 3.77155124092738e-05, \"text\": \"Rhode Island\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.9020824540106664, \"rank\": 0.052480011105261085, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giuliano_Amato\", \"score\": 0.9999