, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 metres\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it took a bit of persuasion to get to the marathon.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"persuasion\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The other thing that was weighing on my mind was 'Los Angeles\\u2026 marathon\\u2026 heat\\u2026 how could I cope with that?\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.783649503121012e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The other thing\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In fairness, Dario did a lot of research in terms of heat acclimatisation and really got his homework done in terms of what I needed to do.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fairness\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"Dario\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"heat acclimatisation\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"his homework\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As it happened, during the month of June, Providence was roasting hot, so I was training in really hot weather.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"score\": 0.9999768590168074, \"rank\": 2.266567194867934e-05, \"text\": \"Providence\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"really hot weather\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The preparation was excellent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The preparation\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need your consent to load this SoundCloud contentWe use SoundCloud to manage extra content that can set cookies on your device and collect data about your activity.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SoundCloud\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"extra content\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"your device\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"your activity\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please review their details and accept them to load the content.Manage Preferences Treacy had decided to still try to win a medal in the 10,000m before the marathon but kept the focus on his track running by setting some scorching 5,000m times that June.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 2182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their details\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"the content\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"Manage Preferences Treacy\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000m\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"his track\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always liked to race myself into world-class running.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world-class running\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I came back to Europe, maybe 10 days before I came back I did a 29-mile run on a really hot night.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"a 29-mile run\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"a really hot night\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I ran a 5k in London, 13:33 and four days later I ran 13:16 and beat Eamonn's [Coghlan] Irish record.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999989834987609, \"rank\": 1.0162815413078028e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 5k\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"Eamonn's [Coghlan] Irish record\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had got myself in fabulous shape and really was ready to roll in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.783649503121012e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fabulous shape\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kept it all very quiet in terms of what I was doing.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always going to wind up running the marathon, there was no doubt about that, but it was just making sure I had the work done before I ran a marathon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"a marathon\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to the Paris 2024 Olympic Games and marking 100 years of Ireland competing as an independent nation, RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 is broadcasting 'Chapters of Magnificence' a series of 11 radio programmes, each focusing on a living Irish medallist.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996812221, \"rank\": 3.184307701082103e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999639010383574, \"rank\": 3.601930678012563e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"